snippet.title: Bubsy in: The Purrfect Collection - First Trailer
snippet.description:
Bubsy in: The Purrfect Collection is in development with Carbon Engine thanks to Limited Run Games.
Coming Soon!

Our guess for the games included:
Bubsy in: Claws Encounters of the Furred Kind (SNES, 1993)
Bubsy in: Claws Encounters of the Furred Kind (Sega Genesis, 1993)
Bubsy II (SNES, 1994)
Bubsy II (Sega Genesis, 1994)
Bubsy II (Game Boy, 1994)
Bubsy in: Fractured Furry Tales (Atari Jaguar, 1995)
Bubsy 3D: Furbitten Planet (PlayStation, 1996)
